\pard\intbl\ql
{The aim of this course is to deepen the knowledge of students concerning 
labour law and its position within the system of Czech law\'2e Students 
will also get to know to practical challenges in the area of labour 
relations and to the possibilities of finding a solution in managerial 
practice\'2e \line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
