}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to: 
\line
\_manage personal agenda, \line
\_contract and cancel labour relations, \line
\_assess validity and effects of labour acts, \line
\_realise basic rights and duties of the employer from the point of 
view of the manager, \line
\_fulfil the duties of employers set in public law (especially labour 
codex), \line
\_negotiate with employee representatives, e\'2eg\'2e within collective 
bargaining\'2e \line
 \line
}\cell\row\pard
